n;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:52.734375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/b95e4/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 256w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/1779b/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 512w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/b95e4/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 256w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/1779b/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 512w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/b95e4/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 256w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/1779b/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 512w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/b95e4/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 256w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/1779b/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 512w,\n/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/4df2fb8adbdce9ddfa1a7c9681fb8f5a/87945/Poker-FB-Post-1024x538.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>We wanted to kick off our 2021 fundraising with a bang! Or should we say with a royal flush? On January 16th, 2021 The PM Group will be hosting the first Charity Texas Hold’em Poker Tournament of the year. This tournament will be benefiting <a href=\"https://sanantoniosports.org/\"><strong>San Antonio Sports</strong></a>, <a href=\"https://sayes.org/\"><strong>SA YES</strong></a>, <a href=\"https://ccyes.org/\"><strong>CC YES</strong></a>, and <a href=\"https://austinyes.org/\"><strong>Austin YES</strong></a>; but these nonprofits aren’t the only ones who will be walking away with cash. If you play your way to one of our two final tables you could win the top prize of $25,000!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>You can visit <strong><a href=\"https://texasholdemsa.com/\">texasholdemsa.com</a></strong> to register now with early bird pricing of $350 or value pack pricing of $1,200 for four players. The event will be held at the Crown Ridge Banquet Hall with registration beginning at 9:00am and the tournament beginning at 10:30. Your ticket includes food and beverages all day, compliments of Black Tie Affairs Catering. Top 18 place prizes include various American Express Gift Cards and top finishers will receive $10,000 entries to the 2021 WSOP. In total there will be over $60,000 in combined tournament prizes!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><span class=\"wp-image-60285 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:34.375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/85b06/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 256w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/bc282/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 512w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/85b06/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 256w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/bc282/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 512w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/85b06/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 256w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/bc282/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 512w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/85b06/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 256w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/bc282/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 512w,\n/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/bc5aa3b733b79be716089c90db4e45cb/f1720/Poker-prizes-1024x352.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>None of this could be possible without our sponsors so thank you to:</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><span class=\"wp-image-60286 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:1024px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:55.859375%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/85b06/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 256w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/bc282/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 512w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcSet=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/85b06/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 256w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/bc282/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 512w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/85b06/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 256w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/bc282/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 512w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/85b06/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 256w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/bc282/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 512w,\n/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png 1024w\" src=\"/static/c85f341062228b0c2eee7adf6ea2f17e/f1720/Poker-Sponsors-1024x570.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 50px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p>Who’s ready to play poker? We can’t wait to see you on the 16th to help raise money for our benefiting charities and see you win big!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-spacer\" style=\"height: 100px;\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> </div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/\"><strong>About The PM Group</strong></a>: The PM Group was founded in 1988. For over 32 years, the agency has continued to grow and is San Antonio’s largest advertising agency. The PM Group’s client roster spans numerous industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date has raised millions of dollars for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations in the last 15 years! In the past 10 years, The PM Group has raised both directly and indirectly over $12 million for these charities. It is our way of giving back to the community that we so humbly serve.</p>\n","title":"Register for the First Charity Texas Hold’em Poker Tournament of 2021","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Register for the First Charity Texas Hold’em Poker Tournament of 2021","url":"/register-for-the-first-charity-texas-holdem-poker-tournament-of-2021/"}],"title":"Registration Open for San Antonio Charity